    "disclaimer": "Past returns do not guarantee future results. This calculator assumes no taxes or fees.",
    "formulaLatex": "\\text{CAGR} = \\left(\\frac{V_f}{V_i}\\right)^{\\frac{1}{n}} - 1 \\quad \\text{ROI} = \\frac{V_f - V_i}{V_i} \\times 100",
